text: Henrik Kromann Toft is an archer from Denmark. He was born on 11 July 1968. Kromann Toft competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Henrik Kromann ToftHenrik Kromann TOFT == References == Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Danish archers Category:Olympians for Denmark
